node.text: An elephant is killed for its ivory roughly every 26 minutes. IFAW wildlife rangers are often the difference between life and death for this iconic species. I’m #RangerStrongFor elephants with @ifawglobal to show my support for the frontline heroes working so hard to change this statistic. #letsgettowork #ifaw 🙌🏽

node.text: I remember living in Dominican Republic with my grandparents as some of the happiest times. My grandpa was so knowledgeable, he was my favorite person to be around, there was always something new to learn with him. He was the best Papa to me and my cousins. I wish we could’ve spent time together this year, it’s hard to believe he’s not here anymore. I know he’s now watching over us from above. I miss my papa Freddy… 🕊🤍
